### DoorBird Controller (internal Web API)
### Base URL is the Haus application server

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv HAUS_BASE_URL}}

### Get current snapshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get real-time photo (JPEG)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/photo
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get video stream URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/video
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Unlock front door relay
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/relay
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Turn light on
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/light
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get device info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/info
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Restart device
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/restart
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get SIP status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/sip
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get active session
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/session
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get favorites
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/favorites
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get schedule
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/schedule
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get history image (doorbell, index 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/history/image?index=1&eventType=Doorbell
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### List notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/notifications
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Subscribe to notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/notifications/subscribe?subscriberUrl=http://example.com/callback&eventType=doorbell
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Unsubscribe from notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/notifications/unsubscribe?subscriberUrl=http://example.com/callback&eventType=doorbell
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Event callback - doorbell ring (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/event/ring

### Event callback - motion detected (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/event/motion

### Event callback - RFID (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doorbird/event/rfid
